TO run the program:
Just type: 
$ make all run clean

to run the program

CONTROLS
--------

1. To speed up, <up arrow key>
2. To slow down, <down arrow key>
3. To turn right, <right arrow key>
4. To turn left, <left arrow key>
5. Change camera, 'c'
6. In the heli view,
		click and drag up, to move the camera up vertically
		click and drag right, to move the camera right and so on
		Scroll up to zoom into the scene
		scroll down to zoom out of the scene

